{
  "_comment": "Enrichment data for map PNGs. MapManager discovers maps by scanning assets/maps/ subfolders — this file only provides display names, spawn points, and size overrides. Keyed by PNG filename.",
  "_spawn_encoding": {
    "green_dot": "rgb(0,~48,0) — used in maps/2, maps/10",
    "red_dot":   "rgb(~28,0,0) — used in maps/6",
    "detection": "brightness<60 AND (g>r+b OR r>g+b)"
  },
  "_folder_rules": {
    "1":    "survival only         (factions=1)",
    "2":    "skirmish+multiplayer  (factions=2)",
    "3":    "skirmish+multiplayer  (factions=3)",
    "4":    "skirmish+multiplayer  (factions=4)",
    "6":    "skirmish+multiplayer  (factions=6)",
    "8":    "skirmish+multiplayer  (factions=8)",
    "10":   "skirmish+multiplayer  (factions=10)",
    "test": "debug only            (factions=2)"
  },
  "_notes": [
    "Adventure mode reads from missions/ folder — not handled here.",
    "random.png at assets/maps/ root becomes the Random Map meta-entry (all modes except debug).",
    "Folder-1 maps have no spawn dots — their spawn_points must be defined here if needed.",
    "Multiplayer and skirmish share the same map pool (folders 2–10)."
  ],
